						<div align="justify">
							Conrgats Gale and Orbit. For the few of you who weren't there last night Haggin decidede he didn't want to run for Taskmaster or House leader so he dropped out. We then had a short debate between Gale and Orbit and then a vote. Gale won 6 - 3 and is now our new Taskmaster. Orbit is now a House Leader of House  2.<br><br>Afterwards in all the drinking Haggin had an excellent suggestion, Roger Wilco! You can get the newest version by clicking the 'Download It" link on up top. When you set it up rember to use wav recording. Right now I am hosting the Roger Wilco server on my computer whenever it is up at 207.5.147.75. There is a password so only Crimson Dragon members can get in, I'm not going to post it here though. E-mail me or ask somone in game if they know. Hopefully will we be able to have someone on a static IP that can have a Roger Wilco basestation open 24 hours a day. Taeil is looking into this right now but the Firewall is give him some problems. Hopefully everything will be set up soon!
							<br>~ <a href="mailto:Boisvertbladesong@hotmail.com">Boisvert Bladesong</a><br><br>
